cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC 

This paper focuses on compressing and accelerating deep learning models for image recognition and object detection tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses optimization methods, which could place it in the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
